# Calculator Program - Basic Briefing

This project is a simple calculator program written in C. 
It performs basic arithmetic operations such as addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division. 
The user is prompted to enter two numbers and select the desired operation. The result is then displayed on the screen.

## Features

- Addition, Subtraction, Multiplication, and Division
- User-friendly input prompts
- Console-based interface

## Usage

1. Compile the C source code.
2. Run the executable.
3. Follow the on-screen instructions to perform calculations.

This program is intended for educational purposes and demonstrates basic C programming concepts.